    <p>• Here, vis­i­tors can en­joy a view of Pung­gol Wa­ter­way as well as take part in ther­a­peu­tic hor­ti­cul­tural ac­tiv­i­ties.</p>
    <p>• The view­ing deck has a green roof com­pris­ing var­i­ous flow­er­ing species, such as the Chi­nese Vi­o­let (Asys­ta­sia gi­gan­tica) and Pur­ple Queen ( Trades­cantia pal­l­ida), to not only help cool tem­per­a­tures, but also at­tract more bio­di­ver­sity to the ur­ban en­vi­ron­ment.</p>

